{"tid":1831951,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"深夜藍絲報警 大堆防暴30秒到場","createTime":"2020-01-20T21:57:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T04:13:42.000Z","uid":287735,"like":1449,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":128,"replies":[{"pid":"4032df19e3e2fff3e8f7b6c2b827e38d8dc16156","tid":1831951,"uid":287735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T21:57:38.000Z","msg":"清晨5點睇緊將軍澳直播<br />\n唔知前因，總之有一堆廢老清緊路障<br />\n現場得返兩個戴口罩手足企係到旁觀<br />\n突然有廢老扔磚，<br />\n記者衝去影但有條友話要叫警察黎check 記者證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一分鐘都唔夠就有幾架狗車黎到幫手執垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photographicsocietyhk/videos/2575736229313383/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphotographicsocietyhk%2Fvideos%2F2575736229313383%2F&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV98VJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=7d1e1df1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photographicsocietyhk/videos/2575736229313383/</a><br />\n<br />\n所以要善用<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港警察嘅職責</span></span><br />\n千祈唔好係條街到跌左一袋垃圾<br />\n再搵第二個人黎報警，<br />\n記得要講<br />\n&ldquo;呢到係XXX，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我<span style=\"color: red;\">懷疑</span>有人準備堵路</span><br />\n，有人將袋垃圾倒咗係地下，快啲派人理處理&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁鍾意話記者唔幫手除暴安良，不如等佢做埋掃街果份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以為冇示威唔洗做好筍？慢慢吹下風先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好咁傻用自己電話號碼"},{"pid":"296763f0894cf28ac47c46cdb9035c4216474af3","tid":1831951,"uid":287735,"like":141,"dislike":2,"score":139,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T21:58:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">支持警察 專執垃圾</span>"},{"pid":"ce3ac73e9d7777de931a42c4d4518782c9ec08a6","tid":1831951,"uid":287735,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T21:59:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"